api_id.description: Kindly obtain your unique Telegram API ID from my.telegram.org and provide it confidentially. Please do not disclose this information to any third party.

api_hash.description: Kindly obtain your unique Telegram API Hash from my.telegram.org and provide it confidentially. Please do not disclose this information to any third party.

string_session.description: Please execute the Python script string_session.py using Python3 and retrieve the generated string session. This session data should be treated as strictly confidential and not shared with any external parties.

command_handler.description: Command handler use pattern matching to detect and respond to specific user input, so you provide a custom handler of your choice.

ciraag_gallery.description: All content saved using Ciraag will be automatically stored in the Ciraag Gallery. To access your saved content, please enter the chat ID of your Ciraag Gallery.

gemini_api.description: To take advantage of Gemini, collect the Gemini API from ai.google.dev and provide it here.
